hot 5.png", "id": "2798915413752699", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982699_2798915417086032_7172758115676658381_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=lCuII2WitXAQ7kNvgE08nKP&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDqvH3N8EQDYwLhrdpNyh6YGk4wB58O_5o6e1_yaUunlg&oe=6724ABCD"}, {"file_name": "EF-VR App Screenshot 7.png", "id": "156438259646824", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974453_156438262980157_1627242679791238025_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=h5NY5I0IdiwQ7kNvgH_h97b&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBznfpjlDejEv_TfZl-HMoCCexclqI6azLt90cu-9VW6A&oe=6724CA6B"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "EF-VR Oculus App Lab Cover Art Landscape.png", "id": "252965883002072", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035424_252965886335405_7319811021161173829_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Mt8vKqwcCKgQ7kNvgHGDLkE&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDKJZt-LnSOsZxul05GJoYqAliLq3k84TB5k1M1-Qhq8w&oe=6724AD9D"}, "display_name": "Edge Factor VR", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Edge Factor's Virtual Reality Experiences are all about experiential learning. VR takes this to the next level, giving students a closer look at interests and industries during their career exploration.\n\nLearn about industries from around the country. Experience tours and demonstrations with industry professionals. Interact with objects, inspect life-size models, and discover a whole new way to learn. Explore gamified experiences with quizzes, challenges, and experimentation to ignite a passion for learning and career exploration.\n\nVirtual Reality  =  High Impact Experiential Learning\n\nAn existing Edge Factor membership is required to access.", "short_description": "Take experiential learning to the next level with Edge Factor's Virtual Reality Experience. Explore industries from around the